H. No. 3731 / 57 OG No. 15, 2652 (April 10, 1961)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 2923, June 19, 1960 ]

AN ACT CHANGING THE NAMES OF CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF PRIETO-DIAZ, PROVINCE OF SORSOGON.

Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The names of the following barrios in the Municipality of Prieto-Diaz, Province of Sorsogon, are changed as follows:

Barrio Cayo to Barrio Santa Lourdes;

Barrio Manao to Barrio San Fernando;

Barrio Visitang-Daan to Barrio San Isidro;

Barrio Cagbulalacao to Barrio San Ramon;

Barrio Binuntulan to Barrio Santo Domingo; and

Barrio Pigbanua to Barrio San Rafael.

SEC. 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted without Executive approval, June .19, 1960.
